%N A395066 Triangle T(n,k), n >= 0, 0 <= k <= n, read by rows, where T(n,k) = [x^k] Product_{j=0..n} (1 + j^4*x).
%H A395066 Seiichi Manyama, <a href="/A395066/b395066.txt">Rows n = 0..139, flattened</a>
%F A395066 T(n,k) = T(n-1,k) + n^4 * T(n-1,k-1).
%F A395066 T(n,k) = Sum_{1 <= x_1 < x_2 < ... < x_{n-k} <= n} ( n!/Product_{j=1..n-k} x_j )^4.
%F A395066 T(n,k) = Sum_{1 <= x_1 < x_2 < ... < x_k <= n} ( Product_{j=1..k} x_j )^4.
%e A395066 Triangle begins:
